'''力學視差'''是從 (周年) [[視差|視差]]計算估計距離的方法。在[[天文學|天文學]]，至一對[[聯星#目視聯星|目視聯星]]的距離可以從兩顆伴星的[[質量|質量]]、[[軌道|軌道]]的大小和彼此互繞的公轉週期來估計<ref>{{cite book
 | author = Patrick Moore 
 | title = Philip's Astronomy Encyclopedia
 | url = https://archive.org/details/philipsastronomy00pmoo
 | edition = revised and expanded ed.
 | year = 2002
 | publisher = Philip's
 | location = London
 | isbn = 0540078638
 | page = [https://archive.org/details/philipsastronomy00pmoo/page/n128 120]
}}</ref>。

計算力學視差，需要觀察到的恆星互繞軌道的角[[半長軸|半長軸]]和它們各自的[[視星等|視星等]]。通過使用[[艾薩克·牛頓|牛頓]]更通用的[[軌道週期|軌道週期]][[立方|立方]]與[[半長軸|半長軸]]的[[平方|平方]]成比率的[[克卜勒第三定律|克卜勒第三定律]]，可以得到聯星系統的總質量<ref>{{cite web
 |url         = http://www.site.uottawa.ca:4321/astronomy/index.html#dynamicalparallax
 |title       = dynamical parallax
 |accessdate  = 2006-07-18
 |work        = Astronomy Knowledge Base
 |deadurl     = yes
 |archiveurl  = https://web.archive.org/web/20060705214728/http://www.site.uottawa.ca:4321/astronomy/index.html#dynamicalparallax
 |archivedate = 2006-07-05
}}</ref>，連同[[質光關係|質光關係]]，可以測量出聯星系統的距離<ref>[http://csep10.phys.utk.edu/astr162/lect/binaries/masslum.html The Mass-Luminosity Relation] {{Wayback|url=http://csep10.phys.utk.edu/astr162/lect/binaries/masslum.html |date=20110720031604 }}, University of Tennessee, Astronomy 162: Stars, Galaxies, and Cosmology, lecture notes.  Accessed July 18, 2006.</ref>。

這項技術，估計聯星系統中兩顆天體的質量，經常以太陽質量為單位。然後，使用[[天體力學|天體力學]]的[[克卜勒定律|克卜勒定律]]，計算恆星的距離。一旦發現了距離，憑藉著掠過天空形成扇形的弧，給與初步的距離測量。 從這種測量和兩顆恆星的[[視星等|視星等]]，並且使用質光關係，可以得到每顆恆星各別的質量。這些質量被用來再計算分隔的距哩，並反覆這個程序。很多時候，當這種運算反覆進行多次之後，距離的精確度可以使誤差小於5% <ref name="double">{{cite book|last=Mullaney|first=James|title=Double and multiple stars and how to observe them|publisher=Springer|year=2005|isbn=1852337516|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=OM3hozlKt9AC&lpg=PA27&ots=da06NVpIY_&dq=Mass-Luminosity%20relation%20distance%20binary&pg=PA27#v=onepage&q=&f=false|access-date=2012-02-18|archive-date=2014-01-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140103133209/http://books.google.com/books?id=OM3hozlKt9AC&lpg=PA27&ots=da06NVpIY_&dq=Mass-Luminosity%20relation%20distance%20binary&pg=PA27#v=onepage&q=&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在注意到生命期與M/L大約成正比，質光關係也可以用來測定恆星的生命期。發現質量越大的恆星壽命較短，更複雜的計算因素是隨著時間推移的質量流失。

